r />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">原來有咁多同路人 <br />\n<br />\n已分手五個月</span>"},{"pid":"2cc5cd73b2ee81fa46e66839dc8e3d87284a797e","tid":92654,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"叫我怎假設從來沒有<br />\n你這對象　即使可當你是朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd69b59a33c91d0a3ac93901faf4e245a0e040f","tid":92654,"uid":1987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:04:37.000Z","msg":"喉嚨很乾"},{"pid":"6e1ef1d9f8cd4f94775270c884251b7daf929913","tid":92654,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:06:14.000Z","msg":"可惜不是你 陪我到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ea33a7862bc9d02a22c53122df57fa047ccc1e","tid":92654,"uid":9003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你千萬不要在我婚禮的現場<br />\n我聽完你愛的歌 就上了車<br />\n<br />\n明明同現任仲算好地地<br />\n尋晚訓覺發夢見到佢 竟然仲係毫不猶豫咁拖起佢<br />\n我係咪以後都要活係佢陰影之下<br />\n我幾時先可以完全放低佢<br />\n雖然好憎佢咁無情咁放棄我<br />\n但我仲係好希望佢開心幸福 如果我唔岩佢 都想佢搵到個錫佢既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係好賤</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有一天晚上 夢一場<br />\n你白髮蒼蒼 說帶我流浪<br />\n我還是未猶豫 就隨你去天堂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cfe39f2e0addcba9acedada5b6c512a348a749","tid":92654,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:14:11.000Z","msg":"我懷念的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823ae18bed1e31ab69bb268d436a10a2eec1ef2b","tid":92654,"uid":65574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T01:19:45.000Z","msg":"傳說中 痴心的眼淚會傾城<br />\n霓虹熄了 世界漸冷清<br />\n煙花會謝 笙歌會停<br />\n顯得這故事尾聲 更動聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":