/span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你係我ex就好.. 好想佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地分開咗5個月 好快就半年啦..<br />\n日日都見面 我根本放唔低你.."},{"pid":"0d48ef734884de0862c019e6b168c781ffc64b19","tid":92654,"uid":58002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"雞全部都係雞"},{"pid":"f1cda94d67d1f2ac0c2f99fe507c9df03f116f59","tid":92654,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"我們在寂寞中靠近 擁抱中痊癒<br />\n卻不敢輕易說愛情<br />\n有些人愛著愛著就變了<br />\n而誓言愛著愛著會忘記<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581cd3936ef859800f2dd23b1b4a84b7296382b0","tid":92654,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"薔薇將秋色 無私的給了多壯闊的地 然而想不起剩下甚麼給你"},{"pid":"ab3aa5f9d7b7d4e1d262f78c9868b040f6c02fe7","tid":92654,"uid":25478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>倘若那天<br />\n把該說的話好好說 該體諒的不執著<br />\n如果那天我 不受情緒挑撥 你會怎麼做<br />\n那麼多如果 可能如果我<br />\n可惜沒如果 只剩下結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">原來有咁多同路人 <br />\n<br />\n已分手五個月</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你係我ex就好.. 好想佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地分開咗5個月 好快就半年啦..<br />\n日日都見面 我根本放唔低你..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同你應該都係被人飛 所以先放唔低人"},{"pid":"9eb657250caa8cf271d3871b2b4e81dfe1ec2b5d","tid":92654,"uid":61250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"時常想起過去的溫存<br />\n它讓我在夜裡不會冷"},{"pid":"32ba94cd7a91a505e4a254eb41cb3a727a4d6a43","tid":92654,"uid":49062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>為未來改正我習慣    忙下去   捱下去  <br />\n但一不小心   總記起你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85749b13d76813bcbeee99e945faaac87c74f398","tid":92654,"uid":7335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"如何回到當時 猶如情侶熱戀的那時"},{"pid":"36cbb28e855ba5208ba8e4210c1e6f30787528fe","tid":92654,"uid":69629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"相愛到不愛 心淡到心開 導致了傷害"},{"pid":"4011419825f1ae1def302e0fe045b1163ea4b5b2","tid":92654,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>倘若那天<br />\n把該說的話好好說 該體諒的不執著<br />\n如果那天我 不受情緒挑撥 你會怎麼做<br />\n那麼多如果 可能如果我<br />\n可惜沒如果 只剩下結果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">原來有咁多同路人 <br />\n<br />\n已分手五個月</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你係我ex就好.. 好想佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地分開咗5個月 好快就半年啦..<br />\n日日都見面 我根本放唔低你..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同你應該都係被人飛 所以先放唔低人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇住佢日日開開心心 真係屌出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afcb305c4bfad646761dbe7e4c4ca2c8bb52f7c","tid":92654,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"我倆已經　是分開不用再更正<br />\n還是有一個她　你真心喜愛到感性<br />\n能遇上多麼好　我不敢憎你　愛沒有保證<br />\n你快樂找你快樂　全部是已經<br />\n<br />\n你叫我怎麼辦　忘記你太艱難<br />\n寧願將眼淚化做每滴血　使你回望一眼<br />\n你叫我怎麼辦　情緒因你急轉彎<br />\n最怕我不再愛別人　已習慣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你揀既 始終都係你現任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你同佢旅行都去完啦 都重唔肯分手"},{"pid":"7082df9ff626d11b02ba89484367c1e60dc80965","tid":92654,"uid":3230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"每次殺不死你 殺不死你"},{"pid":"47e461955cd74d24f026c722a81f3ba496fdcef5","tid":92654,"uid":54513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"你不知道我為什麼狠下心<br />\n盤旋在你看不見的高空裡<br />\n多的是 你不知道的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a20c2d438ffede5e5157917b51f17b407bc630a","tid":92654,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"現時大了 那種心跳難重演<br />\n極燦爛時光 一去難再遇上一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e40c2cd1d6bf5ae26dd6d4288ce6751ff8829b","tid":92654,"uid":14241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"今天起各有逸後<br />\n曾相擁 曾牽手 無需要 定擁有<br />\n願我所愛以後帶著笑口<br />\n別回首<br />\n復原後不要再度跟你做朋友<br />\n我怕我 念舊"},{"pid":"6761b8a75a7452cf9f3120490922e2680c9281bb","tid":92654,"uid":56128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"日後 盡量別教今天的淚白流<br />\n留低擊傷你的石頭 從錯誤裏吸收<br />\n<br />\n唔係特別鍾意單春，但係每次覺得灰心難過嘅時候，就會諗起個時佢喺我隔離唱呢一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5412f87d2202ad20537eb75882ea33bfdade4b2","tid":92654,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"曾掛念某刻跟你邂逅<br />\n緣分尚未夠 甜夢似虛構<br />\n也只怪當天 我怎麼參不透"},{"pid":"b5d34fb6331cd9c96f0876b42268b5f8acc604c8","tid":92654,"uid":4462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"當 這地球沒有花"},{"pid":"c6d64c3cbd6f3f69773d98043bfd7de2c12f2362","tid":92654,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>來年陪着子女學行 記念當初我們的愛情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到呢句即刻喊左😭"},{"pid":"8ae7b527f859372ed526c89c84de9b7c37f3e0f7","tid":92654,"uid":59347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:12:52.000Z","msg":"You`re always everything to me<br />\n看盡人來又去　 我的心能屬意誰<br />\n伴你牽手我叫伴侶　換了雙手我卻是誰<br />\n照樣柔情蜜意　不是你　心虛到　未能面對<br />\n如從來沒你　找不到對比<br />\n期望你也知誰還愛你　大概手都分夠了才再一起"},{"pid":"0b3d7b276ef6fcfcf1209295def59560bac75f37","tid":92654,"uid":6880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r