654,"uid":6484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:11:56.000Z","msg":"我太少解釋心裡感激 讓你擔心不似被愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fd37e421283918c1e35cc83bb1e8bed865118","tid":92654,"uid":65573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:15:43.000Z","msg":"投入過1分鐘足夠一直收藏<br />\n承認共你很相襯 但再沒法一起<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec3469171dd36396e0acb028077ca40f800b78a","tid":92654,"uid":14048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:19:08.000Z","msg":"我爲何未懂得自白 我爲何未捨得學習 <br />\n恃住雄辯滔滔 隨便的把你喝罵 <br />\n我爲何未懂得站立 爲事情出錯了負責 <br />\n然後我 然後我 恨不得當初 <br />\n懂得愛惜你"},{"pid":"37a68fca5ed7230c9c358bb4b76f803eeb474554","tid":92654,"uid":10455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:19:32.000Z","msg":"只期待 後來的你 能快樂<br />\n那就是後來的我最想的<br />\n後來的我們依然走著 只是不再並肩了 朝各自的人生追尋了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9437627e08e719ea201bf75cdd3893eb931fb781","tid":92654,"uid":68631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:44:18.000Z","msg":"不用擔心得太多 我會一直好好過<br />\n<br />\n我會學著放棄你 是因為我太愛你<br />\n<br />\n今日仲要係你生日（香港時間）  祝你生日快樂 永遠都過得開開心 你幸福 就夠喇"},{"pid":"9ab27e1fe4e3060bfdbc9ecc10957f7b5b6d544b","tid":92654,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:47:53.000Z","msg":"內疚 全首"},{"pid":"896e59d270321bbef01ff83652e44b7294d48c05","tid":92654,"uid":44704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T20:21:43.000Z","msg":"生活靜靜似是湖水 全為你泛起生氣"},{"pid":"86d2414cfb9f81075e399235b9a7c3e83a103b5e","tid":92654,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T20:40:14.000Z","msg":"但你與我有過的過去 牽涉後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8ad2c8833c9aa7416bb2fb4dcf39dc5eda11cd","tid":92654,"uid":56597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201